        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Three troubled youths, each from a dysfunctional household, find comfort in each other and form a chosen family. Eldest brother Ling Xiao, second brother He Zi Qiu, and youngest sister Li Jian Jian grow up together, supporting one another through life's highs and lows. After high school, Ling Xiao and He Zi Qiu return to their biological families. Nine years later, the three reunite, but unresolved pasts continue to haunt them. Can\n\nthey confront their personal struggles and become better versions of themselves, or will their histories define them forever?",
